fields.name:
Once I have received the vehicle I will send full vehicle details (vehicle reg, make/model), start and end date & driver name to ecologybusinesssupport@rskbiocensus.com so this can be added to the Motor Insurance Database. I realise that if I do not send these details the vehicle WILL NOT be insured.
I will return the hire vehicle with the same amount of fuel as it was delivered with.
I will complete a vehicle check for the vehicle you have received.
